# 🏥 Hospital Management System

## TechnoHacks Solutions - Java Development Internship

This project was developed as **Task 2 (Mini Project)** during my **Java Developer Internship at TechnoHacks Solutions Pvt. Ltd.**

The Hospital Management System is a desktop-based application developed using **Core Java, Java Swing, MySQL, and JDBC**. It automates various hospital operations such as patient management, doctor management, room allocation, appointments, billing, and patient discharge.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Login Authentication
- Patient Management
- Doctor Management
- Employee Management
- Room Management
- Appointment Management
- Billing Management
- Patient Discharge
- MySQL Database Integration using JDBC

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Core Java
- Java Swing
- JDBC
- MySQL
- Eclipse IDE
- MySQL Workbench

---

